room_title: Escape room "Table 4 2" by Premier Escape Rooms in San Antonio
room_address: 19186 Blanco Rd Ste 102 San Antonio, TX 78258
room_description: It's date night and you have reserved the best Italian restaurant in town. Everything is going well when all of a sudden the lights go out and you are left in the dark trying to figure out what's going on. The staff gives you an old lantern and tells you the emergency security system has kicked in locking everyone in which has been caused by ants terrorizing the electrical system. You decide to take matters into your own hands to get the lights back on and the door unlocked so you can get out of there...
